headline: Freeport Provides Update on PT Freeport Indonesia Operations
summary: PHOENIX, September 12, 2025--Freeport (NYSE: FCX) announced today that expert teams continue to work around the clock to locate seven PT Freeport Indonesia (PTFI) team members whose access routes in the Grasberg Block Cave were blocked following the previously reported September 8 mud flow incident.
